---

---

<section id="nucleo" class="py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-zt-surface/50 -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zt-border to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zt-border to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 fade-up">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-zt-primary/60"></span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zt-primary font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em]">01 / Filosofía</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-zt-dark leading-tight mb-6">
          El rendimiento no es opcional.
          <span class="accent-gradient-text">La estética tampoco.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zt-text/80 leading-relaxed font-light mb-8 text-lg">
          Eliminamos la brecha entre el diseño visual y la ingeniería de software.
          Construimos sistemas complejos que son intuitivos, y páginas web que son
          técnicamente invulnerables.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-zt-border">
          <div class="bg-white/60 backdrop-blur rounded-xl p-5 border border-zt-border/40 card-hover">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-display font-bold accent-gradient-text mb-1">UX</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-zt-text uppercase tracking-widest font-medium">Interfaces Inteligentes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/60 backdrop-blur rounded-xl p-5 border border-zt-border/40 card-hover">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-display font-bold text-zt-dark mb-1">DEV</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-zt-text uppercase tracking-widest font-medium">Código Estructurado</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7 fade-up rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-zt-surface aspect-[4/3] relative border border-zt-border/50 shadow-lg overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-zt-primary/5 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/1200x900/FFFFFF/E5E7EB?text=Wireframe+|+Data+Structure"
          alt="Infraestructura A&A — diagrama de sistema"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 right-5 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-zt-border/60 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-mono font-medium text-zt-primary shadow-sm">
          SYS.REQ_001
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
